HEADWORD: Ratihabition
<hw>Rat`i*ha*bi"tion</hw> <pr>(-h⟦adot⟧*b⟦icr⟧sh"⟦ucr⟧n)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>ratihabitio</ets>; <ets>ratus</ets> fixed,
